//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SQL_injection#Blind_SQL_injection\" target=\"_blank\">blind SQL injection</a> vulnerability which affects all users.</p>\n<p>The plugin was quickly patched and updated to address the issue so make sure to upgrade your website to version 1.7.4 ASAP.<br />\n<span id=\"more-8902\"></span></p>\n<p>Fortunately, we weren&#8217;t affected since we use the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/all-in-one-seo-pack/\" target=\"_blank\">All in One SEO Pack plugin</a> instead. Both are great plugins, however.</p>\n<p>Kudos to <a href=\"https://yoast.com/wordpress-seo-security-release/\" target=\"_blank\">team Yoast</a> for the speedy resolution. I&#8217;m sure all the free press coverage helped their business as well.</p>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?a=uqvspID3eek:l8zRZBQDPkw:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?a=uqvspID3eek:l8zRZBQDPkw:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?i=uqvspID3eek:l8zRZBQDPkw:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?a=uqvspID3eek:l8zRZBQDPkw:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?i=uqvspID3eek:l8zRZBQDPkw:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?a=uqvspID3eek:l8zRZBQDPkw:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?a=uqvspID3eek:l8zRZBQDPkw:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?i=uqvspID3eek:l8zRZBQDPkw:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/appthemes/~4/uqvspID3eek\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:29:\"